    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Experience automotive perfection with this absolute gem! This vehicle is in pristine, mint condition, looking and driving as if it just left the showroom floor for the first time. Every detail has been meticulously preserved, from the flawless exterior to the spotless interior, making it a rare find for any discerning buyer looking for a car that is truly like new.",
