      "description": "We are pleased to present this superlative example of automotive excellence. Maintained to an exacting standard, this vehicle remains in peerless condition, exhibiting the pristine aesthetic and mechanical integrity typically reserved for the showroom floor. Every aspect of this specimen has been fastidiously preserved, ensuring it meets the requirements of the most discerning collector. This offering represents a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of unrivaled caliber and distinction.",
      "price": 44800.0,
